creator: Next edu
descriptionHtml:
Learn English help you learn English words with FLASH CARD easily and efficiently👍, it let you learn English words with FLASH CARD which contain pictures, pronunciation, example sentence, and it let you learn English by topic, by plan; Learn English also provide various tests to reinforce learning.👍

⭐ Learn English features: ⭐
+ Learn English with FLASH CARD, it contain pictures, pronunciation, example sentence, test
+ Learn English by topic: foods, shopping, nature, health, sports etc.
+ Learn English by plan, you can config the number of words you want to learn per day
+ Provide Check-in for learning
+ Learn English provide 3 learning mode: 1. No review 2. Review the day before 3. Review repeatedly (according to Ebbinghaus curve)
+ Support many vocabulary books and word library📚, such as Oxford, Collins, IELTS, TOEFL, GRE, etc
+ Personalized settings to config as you like
+ Support multi languages
+ Support search word, use as a dictionary

Disclaimer:
